<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT7">
<l>iṉṟāka nāḷaiyē yāka iṉicciṟitu</l>
<l>niṉṟāka niṉṉaruḷeṉ pālatē naṉṟāka</l>
<l>nāṉuṉṉai yaṉṟi yilēṉkaṇṭāy nāraṇaṉē</l>
<l>nīyeṉṉai yaṉṟi yilai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Whether it comes today, or tomorrow,</l>
<l>or be slightly delayed now, Your grace is mine.</l>
<l>Look, O Nārāyaṇa! Indeed, I do not exist without You,</l>
<l>[and] You do not exist without me [either].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
